data.description: Welcome home for the holidays! This stunning 5 bedroom 3 bath home bath is ready for your family & friend gatherings! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting open concept interior. The kitchen is the heart of the home, with an island, beautiful finishes, and a dining area open to the living room. With a flexible space that can serve as an office or study and an additional living room upstairs to enjoy! The spacious backyard provides a great outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment, open to additional space offering privacy without neighbors behind. This beautiful home can be yours, schedule your showing today!
